node.text:
Part of my mission is to provide women of color with a no-cost, high-quality education program that will empower them to start and grow their businesses. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
That is why I'm grateful that @keshiaknightpulliam has joined the team and has partnered with @MielleOrganics as our Global Education Ambassador for the 2021 Global Education and Entrepreneurship Certificate Program! ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
We envision a global community of educated, empowered, and successful women who are committed to improving their lives and the lives of others. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
If you desire to be a part of that number, then this program is for you! ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Applicants chosen will be able to take the courses within the program at their own pace! We are providing mentorship opportunities, business development education, and opportunities to acquire VC funding for FREE! ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
If you're interested, be sure to submit your application before the deadline. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Applications are open through June 15, 2021! ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
#morethanastrand #rutgersuniversity #applicationdeadline #keshiaknightpulliam #newarkbusinesshub

node.text:
Get to the next level.  The future is Black-owned. That's why we've partnered with Rutgers University and the Newark Business Hub to bring you an in-depth education program on growing your business into a successful start-up from start to finish.  Applications for the 2021 Mielle Organics Global Education and Entrepreneurship Certificate Program are open through June 15, 2021!  We are awarding 60 scholarships for applicants to take advantage of this opportunity for FREE. That's right! We are providing mentorship opportunities, business development education, and opportunities to acquire VC funding for FREE!! If you have the next big idea, submit your application by June 15, 2021, to step into the next chapter of your purpose. Winners will be announced on June 30. To submit your application, visit www.morethanastrand.com. ⁠
⁠
#MielleOrganics ​#morethanastrand #rutgersuniversity #applicationdeadline #mielleorganics #newarkbusinesshu

node.text: Poof dry scalp be gone….. 🤣🤣🤣 So excited to have some of our legacy Mavens fly in and celebrate our ground breaking ceremony for the expansion of our warehouse an additional 50,000 sq ft but also for the launch of our New Oats and Honey Collection 🙌🏽🙌🏽🙌🏽🙌🏽😆😆😆😆 We had so much fun at the Mielle Headquarters 🤪

node.text: We are breaking ground for our new space!!

BREAKING NEWS **********
We @mielleorganics are pleased to introduce our new Oats & Honey Collection!

This is our most gentle collection and is targeted towards consumers with a sensitive scalp, although it can be used by anyone, men and women alike. 

It helps relieve dry itchy scalp, dandruff, and inflammation. 

Oats and Honey is formulated to be non-stripping and will not irritate or damage your scalp. SWIPE LEFT TO LEARN MORE!

Can you guess the fragrance? There is barely any, we heard you and wanted to make sure we included a non-fragrant product to our family of collections!

We hope that you enjoy this line and the special gift we put inside!

Go to MielleOrganics.com to order yours TODAY!

#mielleorganics #mielle #mielleoatsandhoney

Did you hear the news????? 

The performance ✅
The smell ✅
The ingredients ✅ 
The packaging ✅ 
The time and effort ✅

All of the above. I’ve worked so hard on this collection and it’s finally here!!!!! This is why I’ve been sooo busy but totally worth it!!!! Can’t wait….. link in bio on how to sign up first.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Monique Rodriguez RN to CEO: on July 21, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and people standing.

node.text: I am speechless with this transformation I started working out with @byobgina I was 104lbs now I’m 130lbs . I have been slim all my life people would tell me “ you need to eat more” like that wasn’t offensive. I used to be very active as a young adult but once I started having kids I did not make myself a priority.  I became so focused on raising my family and working and would make every excuse to not go to the gym. I didn’t even realize I was that skinny 😱  but when you have a trainer like @byobgina that believes in you motivates you, spreads nothing but positive energy everytime you are around her and she makes working out fun even though I make faces and groan while I’m there. This is more than just a body transformation it’s mental. My mental health has also been at an all time high because I’m taking care of myself more. I used to let my work consume me and now I’m very intentional about setting boundaries and making sure that I work out 3-4 times a week That way I can give my full capacity to being a mom, wife and a business owner. Now my whole family has joined which is also even more motivating. Thank you @byobgina for being more than just a trainer but for being a friend who pushes me and believes in me even when I didn’t believe that this transformation could take place. No matter what your goals are to lose, gain build muscle, she will help you get there and no this is not an ad but a true testimony☺️
